<p>The Blog feature has built in support to generate a <a href="https://support.google.com/news/publisher/topic/2527688?hl=en">Google News Sitemap</a>&nbsp;which is used for submitting news articles to be syndicated in Google News.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>You can check this box to make the Google News Settings tab appear in the blog edit page so that you can add the meta data supported by the Google News Site Map and select an image for the headline.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The url for the automatically generated News Site Map is http://yoursiteroot/Blog/news-map.ashx, you can submit this Site Map to Google if you are using the Blog feature to post news articles.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Note that the automatically generated News Sitemap will only include posts marked for inclusion on the News Site Map and in compliance with the rules for Google News Sitemaps, it will only include articles published within the last 2 days.</p>
